[{"image":"/images/story68_c_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story68_c_m.mp3",
"text":"開生日會是怎樣的"},
{"image":"/images/story68_p1_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story68_p1_m.mp3",
"text":"小朋友的生日到了，小朋友的爸爸媽媽，有時會為小朋友開生日會"},
{"image":"/images/story68_p2_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story68_p2_m.mp3",
"text":"有時，還會請其他小朋友一起來參加"},
{"image":"/images/story68_p3_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story68_p3_m.mp3",
"text":"開生日會的步驟是這樣的。1.大人將生日蛋糕和食物放在桌子上"},
{"image":"/images/story68_p4_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story68_p4_m.mp3",
"text":"2.大家圍著桌子，一起唱生日歌"},
{"image":"/images/story68_p5_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story68_p5_m.mp3",
"text":"3.生日的小朋友把蛋糕上的蠟燭吹滅"},
{"image":"/images/story68_p6_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story68_p6_m.mp3",
"text":"4.大人切蛋糕分給大家吃"},
{"image":"/images/story68_p7_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story68_p7_m.mp3",
"text":"5.然後吃其他食物"},
{"image":"/images/story68_p8_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story68_p8_m.mp3",
"text":"爸爸媽媽會幫助我學習這些步驟，這樣我就知道怎樣開生日會了"}]
